content:

Also, as far as I can tell, I can’t access the vote team channels on Discord. ?
just gave you access to the channels! and you should get a link soon- likely within next 24-48 hours
hi <@1269333186718990419> I'm sure you will hear from them before Friday
If you haven’t heard anything by Friday morning, please message here and I’ll get it to you

<@1257469301435400238> - I attended data captain shadowing Wednesday afternoon and am signed up for my first regular shift on Saturday. Can I be put in the channel? Never mind if the debrief forms are still being processed.
Hello <@740977201436164177> we appreciate your patience. You will see the channels before your shift on Saturday.
